item.title: CVE-2023-2880|2024-08-02T06:41:02.358Z -- frauscher%20sensortechnik -- diagnostic%20system%20fds101%20for%20fadc%2Ffadci
item.description: Frauscher Sensortechnik GmbH FDS001 for FAdC/FAdCi v1.3.3 and all previous versions are vulnerable to a path traversal vulnerability of the web interface by a crafted URL without authentication. This enables an remote attacker to read all files on the filesystem of the FDS001 device.
